[recv] {"type": "turn_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Considering Docker Images for Neo4j**\n\nI'm contemplating using the Docker image neo4j:5.26.0 or 2026.05.0. I know that the test driver 5.28.8 supports 2026, which is reassuring. I think it’s essential to maintain a deterministic setup for stability, opting for the latest current documentation. However, I should consider vulnerabilities associated with allowed images in GRM. I might also need to look into testcontainers and their supported POM versions, exploring whether they use neo4j:5.26.0-enterprise. I'll check Maven Central for details on source tests.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0583956590347f66016a42576c57c8819398450716fb498f71\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"content\":[],\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqQldxmC2veoJ_75YnFWHiVQhcEhpA8vT6E-9TXhsx7flSM-XgwmGjWzEK0oUfqmA1_VilMug_xIchEeJgOUr8fj7Yw-c9b7bdknatuNvoOAnmk7NFx51UR3gb-BIGIgDcmp0mgvlskSjzCAHRoLYKk_abwf7bg-lYEsBhgLaEuQqD676TElKZ5Axxy3cmsIi_kHcqzRuYXBUyFdGXNLqNNuQ56OdWp0xCmYHysJN77f5uPaBAbSxrls-MqqH18G_oumGurhmiRdpzLTX-sY5cSUdY4lj6JnR9TQnA56WM6UfqpP_jT0fxe2hPusSCDW3vPhQ6peut1KxXDfzVkLet581FnUidt0_BaYHIr_1ScFBQxvxRGOw67-T0p709iLKZJtjNpZeiJRX6EbckHaOAF3rTxId47b1SfIgGYWiZTP3UV1rfGbpcbgJLuODGXhA1lupQH_kYNHrNyXAa6u08I0XEh8daIQuZAnG-vbIauLZvNuqR12PxOtwPZEieFQMG9Rl7ZZRkKx_J5Bvlm_H4Kf-zeAkj9YwKy6VhogXq2rkLGGUe4OMF8_BRaGbd0qJERk0es0c1vJ2v1UfpGhunxaqxPJ4k3a_i63V2uxdtICP60N4PT2ObYEdy7QLOIXjEczHgKdsR7ji-n-ggCe-PnWqelX6c6igu5zjeZ2YDPh4EEKjhqIkuRIdfvtwrIA-QL-TQD_pC4LIQDcZy9EDLCeQ83tgIynQHFjpI_Vc66O_bd3uzsQlcd6NkWVTAZ9oMKPBPSA4OfLVLRBDtcXQPQ0ucFiisUUp3sVlgnQa78nBkhoyHIpEV0aQoTh2pCn9T-2ykinSfbU19kY2Hu3uopYrJxXgIXXE-j_OaYeUlS4SDBEhA7WkhbeNyRa0qxJ_IWpyfK7weWD_GvOKSZhRHN3OzerbXYynv5ERH0G5K4m5SF4fjx9uSsR721tjZpyfyn8Bitcu4A7BDXsVkg2hvZ67HxcWWhfjbH3XSSt1HoAkeOwB8kn70N9B4lMsqj2Cqcpr3PCvbFcVUMZ_TgUehevP0SmbfsAG5SU901jkLdybnwVzgYo6u9avM1jIPAdTply5IbFobAU2crNO0s-GGn6Q3NCX5RRIU2SRE-sNWW0dNJz_9ZHPaiELCFq276vdJ5sxYikm8Fu0HaG